Package: amrr
Title: Assessment Metadata Registry Client
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Damian", "Betebenner", email = "dbetebenner@nciea.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Reads the Assessment Metadata Registry (self-contained annual JSON
    sidecars for assessment-system and accountability-system metadata) into R
    objects, one jurisdiction/system/year at a time. Resolves per cell from a
    local registry checkout (pinnable by commit SHA) or a published static
    bundle, and optionally re-merges accountability achievement targets onto the
    assessment record for consumers (e.g. SGPc) that expect them together.
